    {
      "bookmarkId": "709788_14_2597-2657",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "2597-2657",
      "markText": "观点激进的人往往认为革命才是解决问题的根本办法，但是无数事实告诉我们持不同政见的人倘若能够互相妥协，才是真正双赢的举动。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=709788&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2597&rangeEnd=2657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfc32d305ad49cdfc86e126?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2597&rangeEnd=2657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "709788_3_8776-8807",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8776-8807",
      "markText": "创业之初的艰辛是一种锻炼，没有这份磨炼，也就不会有将来的成功。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=709788&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8776&rangeEnd=8807",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dfc32d305ad49cdfc86e126?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8776&rangeEnd=8807"
